  "war_archetype": {
    "_meta": {
      "anchor": "VOS_Ceiling (quality) + VOS_Career (debut timing) + current age",
      "framing": "Career arc for a player of this profile IF he becomes a real MLBer (career WAR >= 2.0); NOT a per-player forecast. ceiling_to_career.war = MEDIAN non-bust career WAR (typical-if-he-sticks); war_hi = p90 (top-tier outcome). Both binned by VOS_Ceiling among non-bust reachers, isotonic-smoothed. KEY FINDING: ceiling barely moves the typical (median ~8.5 until elite tier) but widens the upside (p90 ~28->42). remaining[_hi] = value * frac_ahead(age) for MLB players, full for prospects. debut_age = current_age + ttd(VOS_Career).",
      "built_by": "analysis/war_archetype_ballpark.py",
      "source": "outcomes.db, 10 cohorts, 403 reached-MLB hitters",
      "caveat": "Ceiling->WAR gradient is gentle (rho~0.15) -> the number is the center of a WIDE cloud. frac_ahead is survivor-conditional -> slightly over-credits older players. Single sim, default settings."
